me.jor.util

类 LockCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.jor.util.LockCache

  • public class LockCache
extends Object
    此类缓存ReentrantLock和ReentrantReadWriteLock.ReadLock ReentrantReadWriteLock.WriteLock 如果要得到一对读写锁，读锁与写锁必须使用同样的key. 一个key对应一个ReentrantReadWriteLock对象或ReentrrantLock对象
